        <h2>
            <span>1. </span>
            Introduction
        </h2>

        <section id="Porpuse">
            <h3> <span> 1.1</span>
                Porpuse
            </h3>
            <p>
                This is a website designed for the lovers of nature, who like to camp and want to visit many places.
                Here they can find a list of campgrounds
                where they can reserve a place to camp as many days as they want,even give feedback about a certain
                place.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section id="Product-Scope">
            <h3> <span> 1.2</span>
                Product Scope
            </h3>
            <p>
                The scope of this website is to provide users a list of safe places to camp ,which contain reviews from
                real users .
                Every camp place is verified by a admin before it's posted ,to prevent fake locations or bad
                conditions.Our goal is to have a comunity of trusting people who can help other people who want to live
                the same experience and go in the same places.
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>

    <section id="Overall-Description">
        <h2>
            <span>2. </span>
